{"tid":1432442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方指暫未收到有關機場集會的申請","createTime":"2019-08-08T08:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T02:52:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c144357f9cf67574fab7fd9e00f20fe2b073d475","tid":1432442,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:49:49.000Z","msg":"警方表示, 過去一日拘捕了3名男子, 年齡介乎22至34歲, 涉嫌昨日在尖沙咀鐘樓一帶, 干犯刑事毀壞及傷人罪, 其中一人今日在九龍城裁判法院提堂.<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科總警司謝振中表示, 留意到未來數日, 會有不同示威活動, 遍及不同地區, 包括明日至星期日, 可能在機場舉行的集會, 他指, 機場是一個人流密集的地方, 呼籲大家集會時和平守法, 不要作出任何滋擾行為, 而警方暫時未收到有關機場集會的申請, 又強調, 警方並不是以一刀切態度處理公眾活動的申請.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20190808162446\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsID%3D20190808162446&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7xZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=053d913e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20190808162446</a>"},{"pid":"66caf0eb19321d713e518c21d1683b07684f3461","tid":1432442,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429285c5efb2fb84d260ce3f1ea0dfd9fce74d4b","tid":1432442,"uid":152976,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:56:59.000Z","msg":"等你清場 比機會你D TG遍地開花嘛"},{"pid":"cc2140d40cfd3fd4ca824384a875b7f435da4d32","tid":1432442,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"429285c5efb2fb84d260ce3f1ea0dfd9fce74d4b","tid":1432442,"uid":152976,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:56:59.000Z","msg":"等你清場 比機會你D TG遍地開花嘛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb5f61867c21c56a4904ce6c7c0ff5